Enhance moduleFactory code for shared RSLs.

Modified Prelink.java to change the module factory code so it will remember what domains have been allowed by a module factory. Later, if any RSLs are added to the module factory, then the RSL code will be automatically updated to allow the same domains as the other RSLs in the module factory.
